iolation of the marginal laws (no-signaling\nconditions) would not for this imply that a superluminal communication would be\npossible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2019 16:38:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-27"}
