5-\\mathbf c_{\\mathrm M})/12$. We also show that the\ngraph distance between typical points with respect to our discrete model grows\npolynomially whereas the cardinality of a graph distance ball of radius $r$\ngrows faster than any power of $r$ (which suggests that the Hausdorff dimension\nof LQG is infinite for $\\mathbf c_{\\mathrm M}\\in(1,25)$).\n  We include a substantial list of open problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2019 17:03:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2019 21:25:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
