ctively compared to an optimum QDI early output BCLARC, and vi) 12.2% and\n11.6% reductions in CT and PCTP respectively compared to an optimum QDI early\noutput hybrid BCLARC-RCA. The adders were implemented using a 32/28nm CMOS\ntechnology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Mar 2019 10:25:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-25"}
