ua in an\nattempt to study the effects of close perihelion passages on cometary surfaces\nand their internal structure, and the potential interstellar origin of 96P.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2019 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 10:15:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
